url: "https://ceep.ai"
abstract: >
  CEEP is a GPU-accelerated FDTD solver for biomedical microwave imaging,
  achieving 20-25× speedup over CPU-based solvers through batched
  computing for multistatic antenna arrays.
keywords:
  - FDTD
  - GPU computing
  - microwave imaging
  - biomedical imaging
  - CUDA
  - electromagnetic simulation
